    <div id="mainContent"> 
     <p><strong>Performing Arts Administration</strong> provides business services, promotional management, and general administration for the Departments of <a href="http://creativewriting.ucr.edu/" target="_blank">Creative Writing</a>, <a href="http://dance.ucr.edu">Dance</a>, <a href="http://music.ucr.edu">Music</a> and <a href="http://theatre.ucr.edu">Theatre</a><em>.</em> </p> 
     <p>We oversee all administrative activities including Academic Advising, Academic Personnel, Course Scheduling, Facilities Management, Financial Reporting, Graduate Program Administration, Payroll and Purchasing.</p> 
     <p>Our offices are located in the <a href="http://campusmap.ucr.edu/campusMap.php">ARTS Building</a>, first floor, Suite 121.</p> 
